  <Nodes>
    <Header Code="HeaderElement1" Type="Subtitle" ShowInTOC="0"><![CDATA[The example]]></Header>
    <Paragraph Code="ParagraphElement1"><![CDATA[<p>Enter item name in 'Added item text' <em>TextBox </em>and set place of added item in ListBox with 'Added item place' <em>NumericUpDown </em>and click on 'Add item' button and the item is added in <em>CheckedListBox </em>on defined position.</p>]]></Paragraph>
    <Header Code="HeaderElement2" Type="Subtitle" ShowInTOC="0"><![CDATA[General Info]]></Header>
    <Paragraph Code="ParagraphElement2"><![CDATA[<p>The example contains demonstrated <em>CheckedListBox</em>, <em>TextBox</em>, <em>NumericUpDown and Button</em></p>]]></Paragraph>
  </Nodes>
